     A*%%TS  SD  20190506  112307  I0777       REL-V7R3M0  5770-WDS
     A                                      TEXT(' ﾅﾎﾞ､ﾎｦbﾓ')
     A            S1SEL          1A  B  5  2DSPATR(ND)
